            <h3>State-of-the-Art Laboratory</h3>
            <p>Aatura Hospital's IVF and Fertility Department is equipped with a state-of-the-art laboratory facility designed to support advanced reproductive technologies and procedures. Our embryologists and laboratory staff utilize cutting-edge equipment and techniques to handle gametes (eggs and sperm), perform fertilization procedures, culture embryos, and perform genetic testing, ensuring the highest standards of care and success rates.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content3">
